      Overview

      The ADWR Bookstore has a new name. From now on, the Departments
      e-commerce location will be known as Water Resources Information
      Central (WRIC). An ever-expanding menu of goods and services is
      featured at WRIC. Thanks for visiting!

      Check out the "Featured Items" section.  We now offer the ADWR Imaged
      Records Database online which includes the Wells 55 database and much
      more.

      SECURE SHOPPING

      Please review shopper info for additional information about using our
      secure shopping basket to purchase products using your Visa
      [visa_small.gif] or  MasterCard [mastercard_small.gif] .  Once you
      reach the "ORDER FORM" you will see the security lock [secure_lock.gif]
      appear in the lower right corner of your browser window.  When the
      security lock is present, the form is encrypted and secure.
      Transactions are authorized by CyberCash authorization Services.  Click
      on any category below to start shopping.  Click here for more
      information about shopping online at ADWR and Internet security.

      start shopping!


